          <li>More enjoyable cooking and entertaining experiences</li>
          <li>Increased energy efficiency with modern appliances</li>
          <li>Enhanced safety with updated electrical and plumbing</li>
          <li>Pride in a beautiful, functional space</li>
        </ul>

